social_posts.post_text: And just like 405 concludes my prs for the year 🔥 hit my goal before the year ended like I wanted to 🤝
Not too bad for cutting 🤷 still trying to keep the bench strength as much as I can 🙏🏼😔

170->215
Atp I’m convinced my legs just purely grew w like no fat gain all through my bulk bc the difference is crazy 😭 went up like 2 whole sizes and they still look lean 😫 only if I trained them seriously would i ever know their true potential 💀
Workin on achieving 1% of Sam’s strength on incline smith 🥲 this was post flat bench tho

Finally did some deads after like 3 months of not doing them and shit was immaculate 😫 not sure if I’ll go back to doing them but maybe here and there 🤔 squat wasn’t too bad after a full day of shingling tho 🤷
A few more pounds to lose and we’ll be here again 😫😫 already down abt 32 pounds🫡

5 hour leg day was too fun😫 looking decent too🫣 was able to hit 545 after months of not deadlifting and this was after heavy squats and roofing🫡 squats were iffy only got 385x3 and did 2 sets of 315x10 but I’m happy w it
115x7 post some heavy bench, been trying to do some more incline now since I can’t really progress the bench while cutting

Deadlift session from last Wednesday 🤔 

515x3 top set. Not too bad for getting back to it
115s and 125s on the incline 🫡 trying to max out The dumbbells at my gym and do the 140s soon 👀

495x3 and some paused sets of 405 

Some decent squats too🙏🏼
Cutting is so depressing on the ego 😔
Late night leg day alone in the dark hits differently when you listen to audios like this ☠️

335x6 not too bad 

Pushing hard to keep as much strength but it’s definitely plummeting😔 might have to say f the cut and just get fluffy again
Cheat meals might’ve kicked in idk🫢
